oma-payment-scheme"}], ["the costs of the Diffuse Mesothelioma Payment Scheme"]}, "” means—\r"]}, {"div", [], [{"div", [{"class", "LegAlphaList"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(a)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["the cost of payments under the scheme,\r"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(b)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["the costs of administering the scheme, and\r"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(c)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["any costs incurred by the Secretary of State to establish a body with whom to make arrangements under section 7(1)(b);\r"]}]}]}]}]}, {"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-the-recovery-of-benefits-legislation"}], ["the recovery of benefits legislation"]}, "” means—\r"]}, {"div", [], [{"div", [{"class", "LegAlphaList"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(a)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["the Social Security (Recovery of Benefits) Act 1997, or\r"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(b)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["the Social Security (Recovery of Benefits) (Northern Ireland) Order 1997 (S.I. 1997/1183 (N.I. 12));\r"]}]}]}]}]}, {"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-reference-period"}], ["reference period"]}, "” means a 12-month period determined in accordance with the regulations, and a reference period may be a period before this Act was passed.\r"]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegAnnotationsGroupHeading"}], ["Commencement Inform