ay, on an application made by the Secretary of State, order the active insurer to comply with the requirement."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-14-3"}], ["(3)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["The relevant court may also order the active insurer to give the Secretary of State other information that the insurer could be required to provide under subsection (1)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-14-4"}], ["(4)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["In this section “", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-the-relevant-court"}], ["the relevant court"]}, "” means—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-14-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the High Court in England and Wales or Northern Ireland, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-14-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Court of Session in Scotland."]}, "\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegAnnotationsGroupHeading"}], ["Commencement Information"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-key-89b740cf4bfb26677189cefea8c2e7ce"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], ["I14"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2014/1/section/14"}, {"title", "Go to S. 14"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["S. 14"]}, " in force at 31.3.2014 by ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "The Mesothelioma Act 2014 (Commencement No.1) Order 2014"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/459"}], ["S.I. 2014/459"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/459/article/3/e"}, {"title", "Go to The Mesothelioma Act 2014 (Commencement No.1) Order 2014 art. 3(e)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["art. 3(e)"]}]}]}]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegBlockNotYetInForce"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegBlockNotYetInForceHeading"}], [{"span", [], ["Prospective"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPblock"}], []}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegPblock"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPblockTitle"}], ["Insurance disputes", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to "}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "U.K.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "section-15"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP1ContainerFirst"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegP1No"}], ["15"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Technical Committee to decide certain insurance disputes", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to "}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "U.K.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-15-1"}], ["(1)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["The Secretary of State may make arrangements with a body to establish a committee called the Technical Committee which, if established in accordance with the arrangements, has the functions given by this section."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-15-2"}], ["(2)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["If a question arises between a potential insurance claimant and an insurer about whether an employer maintained employers' liability insurance with the insurer at a particular time, the Technical Committee has jurisdiction to decide that question."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-15-3"}], ["(3)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["The Technical Committee's decision is binding on the insurer and any potential insurance claimant who was given an opportunity to make representations, unless the matter is referred to arbitration under section 16."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-15-4"}], ["(4)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["The Technical Committee does not have jurisdiction to decide a question that has already been decided by a court."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-15-5"}], ["(5)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["A certificate by the Secretary of State that a specified committee has been established in accordance with arrangements under subsection (1) is conclusive evidence of that fact in relation to the period for which the certificate is in force."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP2Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP2No"}, {"id", "section-15-6"}], ["(6)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP2Text"}], ["Arrangements under subsection (1) may, in particular, include requirements about—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-15-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the composition of the Technical Committee or the appointment of its members;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "section-15-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Technical Committee's procedure or how its p